      "Basic definition of 'living' vs 'non-living'",
      "Understanding that plants are green due to chlorophyll",
      "Concept of food as fuel (from EVS/Class IX)"
    ],
    "previousSessionRecap": [],
    "learningOutcomes": [
      "Define life processes and list the major ones.",
      "Distinguish between autotrophic and heterotrophic nutrition with examples.",
      "Explain the process of photosynthesis as a prerequisite for food chains.",
      "Differentiate between aerobic and anaerobic respiration based on oxygen usage and energy yield.",
      "Identify the role of enzymes in biological processes."
    ],
    "teachingPlan": [
      {
        "minutes": 5,
        "topic": "Introduction",
        "teachingStrategy": "Questioning with simple real-life example"
      },
      {
        "minutes": 10,
        "topic": "Nutrition Types",
        "teachingStrategy": "Comparative analysis and diagrammatic explanation"
      },
      {
        "minutes": 15,
        "topic": "Respiration Mechanisms",
        "teachingStrategy": "Concept development with real-world analogies (burning vs. breathing)"
      },
      {
        "minutes": 10,
        "topic": "Synthesis and Assessment",
        "teachingStrategy": "Guided practice and formative questioning"
      }
