        "misconception": "Plants only photosynthesize during the day and do not respire.",
        "correction": "Clarify that plants respire 24/7. Photosynthesis happens in light, but respiration is continuous."
      },
      {
        "misconception": "Anaerobic respiration produces no energy at all.",
        "correction": "It does produce energy (ATP), just much less than aerobic respiration."
      }
