  "introduction": "Imagine you are running in a race. You feel tired, your muscles burn, and you need to breathe heavily. Why? Your body is trying to get more 'fuel' (oxygen) to release the energy stored in food. Today, we will explore how all living things—from tiny bacteria to giant trees—get this fuel and use it to stay alive.",
